context: <a0_0><b4_0>T<b8_0>he Majapahit Empire<b8_0/><b4_0/><a0_0/> was an Indianised kingdom based in <b5_0>eastern Java<b5_0/> from <a2_0>1293 to around 1500<a2_0/>. Its greatest ruler was <a1_0><b6_0>Hayam Wuruk<b6_0/><a1_0/>, whose reign from <b7_0>1350 to 1389<b7_0/> marked the empire's peak when it dominated other kingdoms in the southern Malay Peninsula, Borneo, Sumatra, and Bali.
